  "text": "We estimate the instrumental variable models using two stage least squares regression with robust standard errors to account for the nested nature of our data [CITATION_1] . Given that antecedents of loneliness are known to differ between women and men [CITATION_2] ; Van den Broek 2017), all estimated models are stratified by gender.",
